  <brief_title>HCV Related Hepatocellular Carcinoma Recurrence After Directly Acting Antivirals: A Randomized Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <acronym>RCT</acronym>
  <official_title>Does Directly Acting Antivirals Usage Affect HCV Related Hepatocellular Carcinoma Recurrence After Percutaneous Ablation: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
