    <intervention_name>Velpatasvir/Sofosbuvir</intervention_name>
    <description>sofosbuvir / velpatasvir will be given for 12 weeks aiming to eradicate HCV. Ribavirin will be added for Child-Pugh B patients or treatment will be extended for 24 weeks for those who are Ribavirin intolerant.</description>
